## ==================== ERROR TESTING ====================

### Missing Required Field - Student
POST {{base_url}}/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch": "Computer Science",
  "full_name": "Incomplete Student"
}

### Invalid Role - Attender (should fail)
POST {{base_url}}/api/attenders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "gender": "Male",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "role": "Manager",
  "salary": 15000,
  "status": "active"
}

### Invalid Status - Attender (should fail)
POST {{base_url}}/api/attenders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "gender": "Male",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "role": "Attender",
  "salary": 15000,
  "status": "pending"
}

### Get Non-Existent Student (should return 404)
GET {{base_url}}/api/students/99999

### Get Non-Existent Employee (should return 404)
GET {{base_url}}/api/employee/99999

### Get Non-Existent Attender (should return 404)
GET {{base_url}}/api/attenders/99999
